        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Our of curiosity, why does the final commit lack the author's full name, present in the commit in this PR?\r\n\r\nGitHub's UI only shows the author in the raw patch view, but nowhere else (apparently).\r\n\r\nCommit in PR has full name: https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/commit/e6c2e4319917edb11a4915f79ef5256773857280.patch\r\n\r\nCommit in master has only first name: https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/commit/57f7d75090a99ff5f7fb71a8c13a0773af32bc2f.patch\r\n\r\nIs this something GitHub is enforcing?",
